The BackTick `` a prefered to use in the JS moderne, cause it offre many Abbreviations than "" or '' :


Backticks :
    String Interpolation =>  Yes (with ${})
    Multi-line Strings =>    Yes
    Embedding Expressions	=> Yes
    Tagged Templates =>      Yes


Quotes "" and '' :
    String Interpolation =>  No
    Multi-line Strings =>    no (Should use \n )
    Embedding Expressions	=> No
    Tagged Templates =>      Often needed

